  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PointingBlockInterface

    public class PointingBlockSlew
extends PointingBlock
    An attitude slew is implemented by inserting a slew block in the PTR. A slew block must be placed in between two observation blocks. The duration of slew blocks is defined implicitly by the end time of the previous observation block and the start time of the following observation block.
